Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:02:00.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto-kun, don't push yourself\Ntoo hard once you enter Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.76,0:02:06.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just vast and little to no street lamps, so make\Nsure to find a place to sleep before sundown.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:11.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And you should take the ferry when crossing\Nover from Honshu to Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:16.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be impressed to see Hokkaido approaching\Nafter you've been on the ship for about four hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.44,0:02:22.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, it really feels like a journey when\Nyou get onto the ferry on your bicycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.70,0:02:28.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This red line is the path of Shin-san's journey...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:31.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks a little like...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:34.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A constellation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:49.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:53.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,School located!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:56.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Where there's a school, there's a store!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:58.74,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord1\be1\frz-16\fs26\fscy70\move(387,162,390,162)\c&H65625C&\3c&HC2B7AE&\frx10\fry30}Ishida Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:57.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:02.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:08.62,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\bord0\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\fscx60\b0\fs38\c&H464949&\pos(175,378)\frz2.939\frx356\fry0}Anpan\N{\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fscx80\fs30\c&HCDCCCC&\3c&H9D8491&\bord1\be1}(with chunks)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:08.62,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\bord0\shad0\fnArtificeSSK\fscx60\b0\fs38\frx356\fry0\frz0.903\c&H393C39&\pos(537,356)}Anpan
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:05.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:06.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But only anpans?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:09.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no variety to choose from!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:13.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's an energy source I've finally come\Nacross! Of course I shall buy them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:16.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, welcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:17.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, I'm buying these!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:21.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is that all you're having for lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:22.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:25.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:25.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:27.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:36.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to slice up more ham?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:39.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. Thank you though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:41.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that I only have pickles ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:45.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And if that's not enough then I only have somen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:45.03,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Note: {\be1\3c&H000000&}"somen" - cold noodle dish
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:46.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, this is plenty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:47.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:53.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This store used to be run by my mother-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:55.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:56.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And the person next to her is my father-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:03:59.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:01.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:03.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are some huge leaves...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:04.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... is that aloe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:05.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:08.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This picture was taken in Los Angeles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:11.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Los Angeles... you mean in America?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:13.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been there, Grandma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:16.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I went there on a trip with my Agricultural Cooperative.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:20.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a snack. Take them with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:24.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But boy did I lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:27.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never even ridden on an airplane before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:30.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Los Angeles, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:33.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What a grandma...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:39.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They were huge! The aloe leaves were like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:43.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even my mother hasn't ever gone outside of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:46.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nor my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:48.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:52.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,His life ended without him ever going out...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:54.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:02.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:05.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This train has a star on it, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:08.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Isn't it cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:10.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This train is called...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:13.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Hokutosei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:13.50,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Note: {\be1\3c&H000000&}"North Star"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:21.00,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuta, this is a sleeper train.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:24.26,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,It runs all night to get to Sapporo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:26.88,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's ride it together someday when you're bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:29.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to ride it now, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:31.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:33.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you get sleepy once it's past ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:37.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Dad would be bored, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:43.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's ride it together when you're able\Nto stay up later and chat with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:46.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday... the two of us together...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:09.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,T-T-T-That was close...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:30.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Milky Way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:39.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A life where he wasn't able to ride even such a tiny red train...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.01,0:06:42.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The meaning to my father's life...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.80,0:06:43.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.26,0:06:46.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The meaning to my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.73,0:06:52.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Arms, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.19,0:06:53.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Legs, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.69,0:06:54.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.86,0:06:59.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:27.97,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}kono sakamichi mo sorosoro PEAK de
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:27.97,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm almost at the peak of this hill,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.97,0:07:32.48,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}baka rashii uso mo kiesarisou desu
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.97,0:07:32.48,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And the foolish lies are about to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.48,0:07:39.94,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}yagate kuru daisuki na kisetsu o omoigaitetara
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.48,0:07:39.94,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}While I thought about the coming of my favorite season,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.40,0:07:45.95,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}choudo ii koro ni suteki na CHORD de
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.40,0:07:45.95,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I hit a wonderful chord at just the right moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.95,0:07:50.41,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}monosugoi takasa ni todokisou desu
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.95,0:07:50.41,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And I feel as if I can reach such wonderful heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.41,0:07:58.38,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}kotoba yori fureai motomete tsukisusumu kimi e
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.41,0:07:58.38,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is for you, who carries on, looking for contact rather than words.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.09,0:08:07.97,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}kona no you ni tobidasu setsunai tokimeki desu
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.09,0:08:07.97,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's a painful throb in my chest that's stirred up like powder.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.97,0:08:17.10,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ima dake wa nigenai de kimi o mitsumetemiyou
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.97,0:08:17.10,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll keep watching you without running away for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:25.65,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}furui hoshi no hikari bokutachi o terashimasu
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:25.65,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The light from the old star illuminates us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:35.37,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}sekaijuu nani mo nakatta sore igai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:35.37,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There was nothing else but that in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:42.80,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}minami e mukau kaze nagareru kumo ni
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:42.80,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If I had entrusted the fragment of my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:51.55,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}kokoro no kirehashi o takushita naraba
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:51.55,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To that cloud floating on the southerly wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:57.69,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(0,300)}kanata e
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:57.69,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(0,300)}Faraway...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:05.78,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArtificeSSK\b0\bord1\shad1\be1\fs35\fscx70\fsp2\4c&H484036&\pos(176,191)\c&HEBE2DA&\3c&H34302B&}The Northernmost Point\Nin Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.45,0:09:10.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... the end of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.45,0:09:13.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.66,0:09:21.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can even reach a faraway place like\Nthis by just moving your two legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:28.51,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}kona no you ni tobidasu setsunai tokimeki desu
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:28.51,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's a painful throb in my chest that's stirred up like powder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.63,0:09:24.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so obvious...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:29.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't realize it until I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.51,0:09:37.73,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ima dake wa nigenai de kimi o mitsumetemiyou
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.51,0:09:37.73,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll keep watching you without running away for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:34.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that I was able to see this view.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.73,0:09:46.40,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}yatara majime na yoru nazedaka nakisou ni naru
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.73,0:09:46.40,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The night is rather somber; somehow it almost makes me cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.40,0:09:41.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.86,0:09:46.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To where you and I... and everyone else belongs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.40,0:09:55.87,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}shiawase wa togirenagara mo tsuzuku no desu
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.40,0:09:55.87,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Happiness can be put on hold but it will continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:49.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.03,0:09:53.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,By stepping down on the pedal the same number of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:10:01.25,hc_insert_jap2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(0,300)}tsuzuku no desu
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:10:01.25,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(0,300)}It will continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.23,0:10:22.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.53,0:10:33.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu, we're going soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.83,0:10:41.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,August 30th - "The End of the Summer".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:45.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, maybe it should be "Their Last Summer Vacation"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.59,0:10:50.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Takemoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:10:58.68,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Sign: {\be1\3c&H000000&}Welcome Back Takemoto-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.68,0:10:59.31,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Sign: {\be1\3c&H4E7CC7&}Congratulations {\3c&H000000&}on Finishing Your Self-Realization!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.31,0:11:00.10,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Sign: {\be1\3c&H000000&}Banzai for the King of Adolescence!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.10,0:11:03.02,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Signs: {\be1\3c&H000000&}Welcome Back Takemoto-kun\N{\3c&H4E7CC7&}Congratulations {\3c&H000000&}on Finishing Your Self Realization!!\NBanzai for the King of Adolescence!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.77,0:11:07.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Takemoto-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:09.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, runaway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.03,0:11:11.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.11,0:11:14.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The Idol of Adolescence has come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:18.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Takemoto-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:21.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad that you're safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:23.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:25.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my, Takemoto-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:28.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you sleep well last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:30.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you did...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.63,0:11:34.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather... we sure let you have a wonderful dream, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.43,0:11:36.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice but to cut them apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.14,0:11:37.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanamoto-kun, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:40.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama, come right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:43.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a huge mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.35,0:11:45.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't wake up at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:47.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.52,0:11:52.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was on a high since I entered Kantou and came\Nspeeding here without really sleeping a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.36,0:11:54.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Hagu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.95,0:11:58.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And how was your journey?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.37,0:12:00.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How far did you ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.91,0:12:03.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... to Wakkanai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:05.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wakkanai... in Hokkaido?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:08.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the very top of Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:10.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And how was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.13,0:12:11.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you able to find yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.92,0:12:13.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your answer? Or truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.59,0:12:15.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you able to attain enlightenment?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.01,0:12:19.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, a lot of people on the way also\Nsaid I was on a self realization...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:22.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I actually didn't leave to find myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.64,0:12:28.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, honestly, I just got stressed out and started\Nriding without knowing what's going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:32.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I just ended up going further than I imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.07,0:12:37.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,While I cooked for myself and made innovations in camping...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.91,0:12:43.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It just happened that I started to have an interest in cycling...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.08,0:12:46.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,On my way, I worked a live-in job...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.21,0:12:49.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And met a lot of people there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:51.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I also thought about a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.38,0:12:57.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't find anything tangible like quotes or myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.72,0:13:01.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I really came back empty handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:04.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Is that so? Empty-handed, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.27,0:13:06.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,With only your adolescence...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:09.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You've seized this moment where you could\Nput things as just "empty-handed"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:12.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine! That's just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.23,0:13:14.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just fine for you, Takemoto-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:20.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The party starts tonight, Takemoto-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.82,0:13:22.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make a lot of tasty dishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.54,0:13:25.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, u-um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,0:13:26.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, th-that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.75,0:13:31.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of a party, why don't we go to the Fall Festival\Nin the Eighth District of Omiya this weekend?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.42,0:13:34.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all eat something at the booths.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:37.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been able to go out anywhere with\Neveryone yet this summer, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:38.43,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, Takemoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:40.51,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\fs24\shad0\bord0.01\be1\fscx80\fsp1\c&H607AC7&\frz16\pos(189,246)\frx356\fry16\3c&H5C8EAA&}Ya{\frz17}ma{\frz19}da {\frz21}St{\frz23}ew
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.43,0:13:40.51,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,You've cleanly avoided the Female Cooking Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:42.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, I should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.68,0:13:45.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've run out of money, so I need to go interview for part-time jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:49.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to an interview, then you should at least take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.56,0:13:52.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You passed out right after you came back last night, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.48,0:13:55.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my gift to you to celebrate your safe return.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:57.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.11,0:14:00.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.28,0:14:07.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlimited use of water is wonderful! On top of that, free!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:12.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, in only his underwear... His face\Nand body are the same color...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.66,0:14:08.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Free of charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.25,0:14:17.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You've sure become wild, Takemoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:19.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This feels great!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:25.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you staring at?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:28.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I just thought that you've lost weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.23,0:14:32.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And this farmer's tan on top of that... so uncool, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.27,0:14:34.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But Wakkanai, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.94,0:14:36.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.40,0:14:39.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't contact us even once for two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.53,0:14:44.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry for making you worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.49,0:14:48.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I wasn't worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:55.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty tough, so I knew that you wouldn't die so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.67,0:14:56.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:14:59.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.55,0:15:02.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting back to the talk of doing well for your interview...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:03.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Before you go...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:07.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cut your hair! For only 1000 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.56,0:15:12.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're doubting my love?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:16.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, isn't it actually pretty dangerous\Nto believe in your love, Morita-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:20.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe! Believe in my pure love!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.53,0:15:21.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's screaming about love to a soaked man wearing only boxers...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:22.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's so transparent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:26.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and smack in the middle of campus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.99,0:15:24.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.12,0:15:28.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about we trade haircuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.58,0:15:30.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only do a crew cut though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.91,0:15:33.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's competing on equal grounds with Morita...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:35.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You've really become manly, Takemoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.50,0:15:35.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.93,0:15:47.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.47,0:15:51.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that was pretty quick for a trip around Hokkaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.73,0:15:55.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all tanned... the top of your nose is peeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.06,0:15:56.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How uncool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:16:00.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have enough money? Want\Nto work two or three more days?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:02.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, please cook us dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:03.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And bentos!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.53,0:16:03.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.99,0:16:05.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:09.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need the bicycle anymore. I'll give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.54,0:16:11.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can ride it home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.16,0:16:13.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and Takemoto-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.71,0:16:14.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:19.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to come work for us, you should get\Nyour driver's license while you're still in school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.88,0:16:24.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ayu, what should we eat first?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.59,0:16:25.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, we'll start with the small things!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.97,0:16:27.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the saucy stuff awaits us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:29.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get the okonomiyaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.39,0:16:30.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan, go for the takoyaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.93,0:16:32.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto-kun, get the yakisoba!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.06,0:16:32.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.64,0:16:34.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san, to the American dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:36.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone gather here once you've bought your stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.35,0:16:38.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And get extra sauce on everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:38.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:48.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Mayama. I get this feeling that\NI saw the same scene last year...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.66,0:16:51.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence... I feel that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.91,0:16:56.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And actually, just how long am I supposed to\Nbe drinking alcohol with just you, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.21,0:17:01.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I missed again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.34,0:17:02.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.92,0:17:05.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I want the Whip-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.85,0:17:14.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.18,0:17:15.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:16.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Show them your skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.35,0:17:20.81,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\be1\fscy85\shad0\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fs28\frz346.931\c&H556370&\pos(180,95)\3c&HFFFFFF&}Big Prizes
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.35,0:17:20.81,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1.5\be1\fscy75\shad0\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fs33\fsp8\c&HA4DCDA&\3c&H9EB2A3&\pos(402,103)\frz359.462\frx8\fry0}Ball Darts
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.02,0:17:20.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You should do it for them, Mayama-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:22.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.11,0:17:24.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm drinking with Hanamoto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.61,0:17:26.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.78,0:17:30.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto-kun, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.82,0:17:32.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.58,0:17:34.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.73,0:18:02.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan, how's your fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.27,0:18:04.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone down now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.94,0:18:07.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:12.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You went really far, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:14.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.41,0:18:19.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What was the end of this land like?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.00,0:18:22.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There was nothing there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.00,0:18:25.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But... it was bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.76,0:18:31.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky was beautiful, and it made me\Nwant to show it to you, Hagu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.01,0:18:36.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that I want to see it through your drawings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.14,0:18:40.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:42.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to draw it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.94,0:18:48.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How far can I go without looking back?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:55.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally understood the reason I started\Nriding on that day while thinking that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.91,0:19:03.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I just wanted to understand how important\Nthe things that I'm riding away from are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.00,0:19:06.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.05,0:19:09.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:33.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto-kun, thank you for coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.28,0:19:40.33,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Box: {\be1\3c&H000000&}For Biking & Camping !!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.46,0:19:52.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your feverish hand was hot and quickly\Nbecame sweaty as I clasped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.80,0:19:58.64,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}atatamesugita omoi o zenbu
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.80,0:19:58.64,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The landscape that we can see
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:54.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It felt alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:56.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It made me feel like I can keep on living.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.26,0:20:01.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to say from the depths of my\Nheart that I'm glad to have come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.64,0:20:03.56,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}hakidashite mieru LANDSCAPE
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.64,0:20:03.56,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By throwing up all the overheated emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.27,0:20:06.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep riding while holding onto those that are precious to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.10,0:20:11.03,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}hantoshi ijou kusuburaseteru
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.10,0:20:11.03,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Igniting the image...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.90,0:20:09.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Onto the unmanageable future...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:11.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncertainties...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.03,0:20:15.53,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}IMAGE ni hi o tomoshite
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.03,0:20:15.53,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That had been smoldering for over half a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.28,0:20:13.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Confusions...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:15.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Unrequited feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.53,0:20:20.45,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}nandakke nakushiteshimatta mono
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.53,0:20:20.45,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What was it that we lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.70,0:20:18.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes that won't come true...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:22.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yourself... unable to leave everything behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:23.62,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}soredemo iin da tte
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:23.62,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even then, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.58,0:20:26.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even those days when you just can't find an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.62,0:20:31.17,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}bokura no inryoku de hikiai motomeau no darou
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.62,0:20:31.17,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We attracted each other with our gravity, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:30.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.17,0:20:37.09,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}sore wa WALTZ no you da ne suteki sa
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.17,0:20:37.09,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's like a waltz isn't it? It's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:33.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Mayama-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.84,0:20:37.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up. The party's started.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.18,0:20:39.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.09,0:20:43.43,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}tsubuyaku you na saezuri kikinagara
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.09,0:20:43.43,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}While listening to that whisper of a song...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.35,0:20:41.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto-kun, do you have any juice?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.47,0:20:43.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:49.73,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}marude WALTZ no you ni ne futari ga
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:49.73,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Something the two of us draw out...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.77,0:20:53.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The refrigerator in my room is still empty as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.73,0:20:55.70,hc_insert_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(0,300)}egakidashite yuku mono
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.73,0:20:55.70,hc_insert_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(0,300)}As if in a waltz.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.57,0:20:56.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't hear that sound anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.95,0:21:02.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel that I can keep believing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:09.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That even the thing all of us were looking\Nfor but never found on that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:12.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.51,0:21:14.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.01,0:21:27.85,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}akanai mabuta kosutte mieru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.01,0:21:27.85,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}I rub my heavy eyelids to reveal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.94,0:21:33.02,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}pastel moyou no mirai ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.94,0:21:33.02,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}A future in the shape of pastels
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.36,0:21:40.12,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}chiribamerareta kigou o tadoru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.36,0:21:40.12,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}I follow the scattered symbols
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:44.24,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}taguri yoseta hyoujou
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:44.24,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}As my expressions were pulled in closer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:50.00,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}nee nandakke sagashiteita mono
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:50.00,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}Say, what was it that we were looking for again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.50,0:21:53.09,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}are wa soune itsudakke
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.50,0:21:53.09,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}That's right, exactly when were those days
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.09,0:22:00.47,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}bokura ga inryoku ni sakarai nagara deatta koro
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.09,0:22:00.47,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}When we used to meet, denying the attraction\Nthat was forming between us?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.47,0:22:06.39,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}sore ga waltz no you dane fushigi sa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.47,0:22:06.39,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}It's like a waltz, isn't it? It's quite marveling
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.39,0:22:12.61,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}sasayaku youna komorebi no kousaten de
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.39,0:22:12.61,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}We paint away sceneries
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.73,0:22:18.78,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}futari waltz no youni ne mawari nagara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.73,0:22:18.78,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}As we waltz and spin
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.03,0:22:24.95,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}egaki dashite yuku mono
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.03,0:22:24.95,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}Where the whispering sunlight falls through the trees and meet.
